author: ekoneil
msg: This adds sort(able|down|up).gif images that are used to display the sort direction of a grid column and are clickable to change that direction.  There is one API change here that switches the value of the "datagrid.resource.path" property in the default data grid property file from:
so that the provided framework sort images can be referenced.  The value of this property can be overridden by using the <netui:behavior> tag.
These icons are apt to change a couple of times as the color / gradient is tweaked so that they're generally usable on dark / light backgrounds, etc.  All of the icons are 96x96 pixels.
Thanks to Troy Beecroft for willingly creating them.  :)
